Ripping the inbedded feather from her arm, as liquid started to flow from the 
wound. 

With a wild & angered look in her glowing crimson optics, she then hurled the 
feather at Tyrael with as much force as she was capable of producing. 
"Arrr-RAGGHHH!!!"

The attempt was to get him out of the sky & to the ground to face her. What 
was another battle. She had be in thousands of them. Some with little or no 
damage, others damaged to the point of stasis lock & a complete overhaul. 

"FACE ME, COWARD!"

--part1_79.14e551d7.2c3b9a00_boundary
